(December 10, 1959) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Henry Beene, Appellant.

Judgment of conviction affirmed. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin and Bergan, JJ.; Stevens, J., dissents in part and votes to dismiss the fourth count of the indictment on the ground of insufficient proof.
